    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/7cd5828cd46295dc78237605816a08ae.poster.avif?t=1772280644\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/7cd5828cd46295dc78237605816a08ae.webm?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/7cd5828cd46295dc78237605816a08ae.mp4?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/849cb7c044946f9f95dd9eda3041b2e1.webp?t=1772280644\" width=645 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/d13617e1b99ffe39abd45c40992b5b5a.poster.avif?t=1772280644\" width=614 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/d13617e1b99ffe39abd45c40992b5b5a.webm?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/d13617e1b99ffe39abd45c40992b5b5a.mp4?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你为 <strong>Omni Mercs</strong> 工作。 当殖民地陷落时，你将被召唤。 你的任务是清理战场并消灭所有摧毁人类定居点的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用丰富的武器库，建立你的基地，对抗一波又一波的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/e8c7dfc2b49b895d2c7c67819e1ff2a5.webp?t=1772280644\" width=645 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/35ab9c0d431278f71a0a65cee6f22ba0.poster.avif?t=1772280644\" width=614 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/35ab9c0d431278f71a0a65cee6f22ba0.webm?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/35ab9c0d431278f71a0a65cee6f22ba0.mp4?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造终极基地。部署强大的炮塔和关键设施，如克隆装置、雷达系统等，打造坚不可摧的防御工事。<br>放置不可摧毁的节点，构建致命迷宫，封锁敌人的关键路线，彻底掌控战场。<br><strong>战略规划和快速反应是你最强大的武器——生存、适应、征服！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/4de746d288699e934a280c6ca01673b9.webp?t=1772280644\" width=645 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/954718deac03ebeec971f62aaa68f269.poster.avif?t=1772280644\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/954718deac03ebeec971f62aaa68f269.webm?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/954718deac03ebeec971f62aaa68f269.mp4?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制你的战斗风格，解锁并调整技能，打造专属于你的战斗策略！<br>四大独特职业，每个都拥有强大的专属技能。<br>选择技能和增益，塑造你的角色优势——<strong>胜利之路，由你决定！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/ecfd55bd629b15dcc359b3723363e7ac.webp?t=1772280644\" width=645 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/30e33040a35bd56614d478c523fd0a15.poster.avif?t=1772280644\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/30e33040a35bd56614d478c523fd0a15.webm?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169510/extras/30e33040a35bd56614d478c523fd0a15.mp4?t=1772280644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友合作，共同迎战！支持最多 4 人 <strong>合作模式</strong>，与队友并肩作战，对抗无尽的敌潮！<br><strong>制定战术、组合技能、掌控战场</strong>——队友越多，战斗越混乱！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >海量武器库</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 <strong>10 种不同武器</strong> 抵御成群来袭的敌人，每种武器都拥有 <strong>双重射击模式</strong>！<br>巧妙搭配武器组合，打出最大伤害连击。 <strong>一把武器装填时，另一把持续射击——真正的疯狂战斗！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战役模式 &amp; 生存模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战役模式中完成一项项高难度任务，或在生存模式中挑战极限，看谁能存活更久！<br>排行榜系统，让你与全球玩家一较高下！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适应敌人，调整战略</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些敌人是蛮力冲锋，有些会将你拖入尸潮，还有些在死亡后会制造更多敌人。<br>了解你的对手，优先消灭最具威胁的目标！ 建立最有效的防御工事，以最小代价消灭蜂拥而至的敌军！</p>",
